"v. 纵容，过分关怀 【英】 v. 纵容，过分关怀(to treat with excess or extreme care) 【同】 近形词: hamper(妨碍; 大篮子); tamper(损害, 窜改); camper(露营者) 【例】 pamper one's child(娇惯孩子) v. 纵容; 娇生惯养 【参】pamper会hamper(v 妨碍; n 大篮子)小孩的成长. 【区】tamper(v 窜改); camper(n 露营者) 【记】原指使吃得过饱，音：胖胖，使自己的孩子成了小胖胖，太关心娇惯了 【相关】hamper 妨碍，pamper 会起hamper妨碍的作用 pamper (v.)  late 14c., ""to cram with food,"" probably from Middle Dutch (compare West Flemish pamperen ""cram with food, overindulge;"" dialectal German pampen ""to cram""), probably from frequentative of root of pap (n.1). Meaning ""to overindulge"" first attested 1520s. Related: Pampered; pampering."
